{"tid":1437550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"8.9 「和你飛」集會 假保安？","createTime":"2019-08-09T14:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T14:38:23.000Z","uid":267625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3b0a08b68786fe8f397e1f54150d5491e4583a69","tid":1437550,"uid":267625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:28:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/503084439752305/posts/2425388500855213?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F503084439752305%2Fposts%2F2425388500855213%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=e8c7e955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/503084439752305/posts/2425388500855213?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"51b649931fbe036714d96f00e983efb52246a137","tid":1437550,"uid":267625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b0a08b68786fe8f397e1f54150d5491e4583a69","tid":1437550,"uid":267625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:28:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/503084439752305/posts/2425388500855213?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F503084439752305%2Fposts%2F2425388500855213%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=e8c7e955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/503084439752305/posts/2425388500855213?sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"轉自中大學生報<br />\n<br />\n【8.9  「和你飛」機場集會】<br />\n<br />\n本報記者留意到現場有身穿粉紅色及黑色polo上衣，掛「Security 保安」的證件，但沒有任何證明文件證明他們屬機場保安，有部分甚至連證件亦沒有戴上，只穿粉色polo上衣（見圖二）。記者向其中一人查詢時，他們稱自己是臨時聘請的保安，負責協助管制人流。同時又補充，他們的工作也負責檢查旅客護照和登機證，意味著他們可以見到旅客的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n記者再向身穿制服的機場保安詢問，保安表示不知誰聘請這些臨時保安，甚至不知道這些人在這裡做什麼，只知道要與他們一起共事：「佢（臨時保安）有佢做（處理人流管制），我有我做。」"},{"pid":"7254f893e08a4383c4b6b65c1d713ae117a16cf8","tid":1437550,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:33:11.000Z","msg":"無人知佢邊個都可以周圍睇人旅行證件，衰撚過軍政府"},{"pid":"ef4f8c986f0328cc38cabcaadf492824b76d0b0b","tid":1437550,"uid":267625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:38:23.000Z","msg":"［响fb見到］<br />\n<br />\n真係「臨時聘請的保安」？抑或係「退役犬」？呢幾條友點睇都唔似普通呀叔，咁嘅年紀，身型keep到，冇啤酒肚，直覺話俾我知，係保安公司請嘅退役犬，反正退咗役，無所事事，手痕痕頂返一兩更嚟過下癮，好合理吖。<br />\n<br />\n有冇機場做嘅fact check下？"}]}